<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px; }
    .header { background-color: #3b82f6; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { padding: 30px; }
    .role-badge { background-color: #f3f4f6; color: #1e40af; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 30px; }
    .button { background-color: #3b82f6; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>New Access Granted</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>Your access levels in the DIFMO CRM have been updated. You have been assigned the following roles:</p>
      
      <div class="role-badge">
        {{roles}}
      </div>

      <p>Your dashboard has been automatically updated with new modules corresponding to these roles. These modules stack together, providing you with a unified control center for your specific responsibilities.</p>

      <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;">
        <a href="https://difmo-crm-frontend.vercel.app/login" class="button">Access Unified Dashboard</a>
      </p>

      <p>If you have any questions regarding your new permissions, please contact the IT department or your direct manager.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} DIFMO Billing System. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
